{"tid":1562544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山齊士已廢！連《FIFA 20》數據都慘不忍睹...","createTime":"2019-09-12T04:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:11:44.000Z","uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d7994cc1a25bfbd697910057d5b050c855ed7129","tid":1562544,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"　　曼聯球星山齊士（A.Sanchez）下滑的有幾厲害？就連遊戲數據也顯現出了這種趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n　　《FIFA 20》中的球員數值設置，山齊士的數據下滑到了歷史最低，總評分僅有82分，相比上季的87分，這個跌幅實在不小。而在他巔峰時期，他在《FIFA 18》中的評分一度達到89分，是世界球壇頂尖幾人之一。<br />\n<br />\n　　相比上季，山齊士的「速度」下降不多，為81，但「帶球」和「射門」這兩項都掉了5個分值。現實中，在曼聯的18個月時間裡，他只攻入過5球。<br />\n<br />\n　　在《FIFA 20》中，同樣跌幅達到5分的還有馬迪（N.Matic）（如今為81分）、保方（G.Buffon）、列治史迪拿（S.Lichtsteiner）和馬里奧-高美斯（M.Gomez），而跌幅最大的是摩納哥後衛納爾多（Naldo），掉了6分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTWc9fY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTWc9fY.png&h=8561ce01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4c4c29ab001c16de8fe36dae60c0c91ef8adc78","tid":1562544,"uid":5549,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"比多左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de603973515ab776af14402d1b164c3d7a3cdfe","tid":1562544,"uid":51371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:00:15.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},{"pid":"c1991923110ad29cba475f575006e836e233eef7","tid":1562544,"uid":5649,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"有歐霸唔踢走去踢歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抵佢數據差左"},{"pid":"28c1e4361e62459b75ce412952e30f6acebe0155","tid":1562544,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmo